content: borisudovicic: Focused on strategic planning and foundational improvements, creating four issues including "Consistency & Stability" (elizaos/eliza#5934), "Add Eigen TEE Deployment Option" (elizaos/eliza#5986), and "Cloud API Plugin for Framework LLMs" (elizaos/eliza#6049), all of which were subsequently closed, alongside an open issue to "Standardize Logging Across Core, CLI, and Server" (elizaos/eliza#6073).
